{"tid":1040981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問蚑那變革者(會員#209487)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?","createTime":"2019-02-28T13:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T14:32:18.000Z","uid":48234,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fc410b7ab1dbebe708890ce20b8b1dd9c070242b","tid":1040981,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a7a8e99521c77689d4b9652024b225d1fc9206","tid":1040981,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5934db6b538128ed9ac7ab5d946c056367f7fc3d","tid":1040981,"uid":130695,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:41:04.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖左，件垃圾仲未死咩？<br />\n我見佢老母日日吊係廣場任人騎<br />\n個老豆仲笑哂口咁一蚊一蚊咁執<br />\n仲有啲主人帶哂動物黎<br />\n掉低張100 哇 個場面幾震撼<br />\n然後佢老豆仲問個主人可唔可以屌埋佢<br />\n買一送一咁喎<br />\n點知個主人叫佢奶返乾淨滴落地啲精同屎<br />\n佢老豆仲口upup 話呢鋪發達啦<br />\n我咁大個人都未見過泥沙地都變鏡面<br />\n呢件垃圾聽講係之前唔知點生出黎既<br />\n我都幾同情佢嫁，日日靠奶老母個臭閪<br />\n同老豆爭食 咁都養得大<br />\n果然中国多奇人"},{"pid":"cefb6ef9eac0ed61211a55ecde533ab0d777cf93","tid":1040981,"uid":28624,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"終極5毛"},{"pid":"008295ac8402040d2eb549e0414359b1026d35b0","tid":1040981,"uid":200521,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母嗰陣用中間嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923fc5257ef37083a639e1af54ef01f079d703d8","tid":1040981,"uid":78143,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T20:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3EJ8O3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3EJ8O3.gif&h=c81dca8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"464255b842063dd6d389c5abfc915e484745805c","ti